latestIgtvVideos.title: " This Matters "
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
More than half of our youths in Nagaland are unemployed and the question comes up , why ?
Why are people unemployed? 
Why can't we get work?
Other than government jobs what else is there?
A lot actually .
There are a lot of other forms of work 
That the young people can do ,
All it requires is ideas and hard work .
.
Got the opportunity to interview these successful entrepreneurs who are setting new standards and goals for society. It was an amazing opportunity and privilege to be a part of this video.
.
.
For more queries , you can head to @entrepreneursassociates .
We are always open to listening to your stories ,struggles and encourage you to persist.
.
.
